sentences.english: The 2.6.25 implementation will need to walk the retransmission queue from the start in order to find this data.
sentences.chinese: 的實現需要從起點遍歷重傳隊列以便找到數據。

sentences.english: Working with the right queue is the task of the adapter configuration, as detailed above.
sentences.chinese: 調用正確的隊列是適配器配置的工作，如上文中所述。

sentences.english: Not all properties are appropriate for all versions of queue manager.
sentences.chinese: 並非所有屬性都適合於所有版本的隊列管理器。

sentences.english: With an asynchronous model, the queue itself acts as a relief valve.
sentences.chinese: 藉助異步模型，隊列本身可以充當一個減壓閥。

sentences.english: Consider creating scripts to automate the regular maintenance of queue managers.
sentences.chinese: 考慮創建腳本來自動化隊列管理器的定期維護。

sentences.english: Now, receive the message from the queue.
sentences.chinese: 現在，我們嘗試從隊列接收消息。

sentences.english: There is also an additional global run queue where new threads are placed.
sentences.chinese: 還有一個附加的全局運行隊列，其中放的是新的線程。

sentences.english: In this report the cases of leptospiral cerebral arteritis were studied with the method of cohort studies.
sentences.chinese: 本文用隊列研究方法研究了鉤體腦動脈炎。

sentences.english: An encrypted message cannot be decrypted by the destination queue manager.
sentences.chinese: 加密的消息不能由目標隊列管理器解密。

sentences.english: What do the lucky ones at the front of the line think?
sentences.chinese: 那麼排在隊列前面的人又會是怎樣的想法呢？

sentences.english: Policy determines the wait time when no applicable message is present on the queue.
sentences.chinese: 當隊列上沒有適用的消息時，由策略決定等待時間。

sentences.english: Note that queue task names must be unique.
sentences.chinese: 請注意隊列任務名稱必須是唯一的。

sentences.english: The final step is to configure the queue manager for triggering.
sentences.chinese: 最後的步驟是配置隊列管理器以進行觸發。

sentences.english: You have to configure the queue for publishing and define the topics.
sentences.chinese: 爲發佈和定義主題，必須對隊列進行配置。

sentences.english: On only 10% of occasions were queue-jumpers physically ejected from the line.
sentences.chinese: 只有10%的場合，“插隊者”被從隊列中趕出來。

sentences.english: Before you do anything, you need a queue manager and some queues.
sentences.chinese: 首先，您需要一個隊列管理器和一些隊列。
